{"tid":523881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"d私樓撚好恐怖 一陣虐殺親生仔女 一陣又虐工人姐姐","createTime":"2018-01-09T04:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T04:50:39.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e506a6e945e83fadedf6a6712e68a36710c66c","tid":523881,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"根據非正式統計 私樓特別外凶宅<br />\n好可怕 供樓供到心理唔平衡😰"},{"pid":"583390bc20f8591f7e6d5eafab987b6d369ae699","tid":523881,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"我地公屋富戶又然一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d19b501f155211eb000b103eed8d509fbe60b42","tid":523881,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"583390bc20f8591f7e6d5eafab987b6d369ae699","tid":523881,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"我地公屋富戶又然一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"我村屋架👍🏻"},{"pid":"d1eadf46427b7913618cee66b63806aa03f48b37","tid":523881,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"建議政府要向所有供樓超過25年以上 <br />\n同做7成按以上人士 提供心理輔導<br />\n否則香港真係好多計時炸彈😵"},{"pid":"b1b67544ca8ac4d7cee73f86e688590ccaef4a33","tid":523881,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"😅"},{"pid":"24c86523244279a6c43c4bed888f7bc8fbc9f94c","tid":523881,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點會住私樓丫"},{"pid":"5188795cb8cbe765055c9892f48834fc4798833a","tid":523881,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c86523244279a6c43c4bed888f7bc8fbc9f94c","tid":523881,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":